{"tid":1981383,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"疑策劃汽油彈襲葵涌警署  警長涉妨礙司法公正被捕","createTime":"2020-04-20T15:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T16:01:57.000Z","uid":141060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"44817862ace786ab0ae2741f56cfd2a9c441a4d4","tid":1981383,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:40:24.000Z","msg":"疑策劃汽油彈襲葵涌警署  警長涉妨礙司法公正被捕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200420/bkn-20200420222723032-0420_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200420%2Fbkn-20200420222723032-0420_00822_001.html&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=bc58ecbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200420/bkn-20200420222723032-0420_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葵青警區一名警長涉嫌妨礙司法公正，今日被新界北總區重案組拘捕。事緣本月13日葵涌警署發生險遭投擲汽油彈案件，警方及時拘捕一名青年，制止爆炸案發生，警方之後接獲指控，指是有警務人員自編自導事件，安排有人於犯案後採取拘捕行動，雖然指控未必真確，但葵青警區為秉公辦理，主動作出調查，並將案件交由新界北總區處理。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，揭發今次案中案，是由於葵青警區繼續就擬施放汽油彈案作出調查，與此同時，收到相關投訴，指有警務人員疑安排被捕人士投擲汽油彈，並在及時作出拘捕，雖然只是指控，但葵青警區管理層已震怒，認為必須嚴肅處理，絕不姑息，案件交予新界北總區重案組調查後，今晚拘捕一名38歲警長，他目前仍被扣查。<br />\n<br />\n更多勁爆猛料，請下載《東網》APP：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2w9ebqD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2w9ebqD&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=587c2594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2w9ebqD</a>"},{"pid":"e6e2728823891292c3449657764d118f49f4bfa9","tid":1981383,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但葵青警區為秉公辦理，主動作出調查，並將案件交由新界北總區處理。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d7f9877d7d4244ba94895b892082deb42dbb70","tid":1981383,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:50:32.000Z","msg":"陣間就放出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1b19a901aead766293a8b96a40879693c16c10","tid":1981383,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:58:38.000Z","msg":"想升職示威活動出去打大力D咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解要以身試法"},{"pid":"90c4c8f261619e0b0c75c1b1f146ad28c2f1d13d","tid":1981383,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"葵青警區管理層已震怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd480aaa594793b58f0912a810c209200633bd4","tid":1981383,"uid":129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"肯撚定係俾人排擠開<br />\n唔洗開心<br />\n黑社會依然係死全家"},{"pid":"3687c1a3d3d4778ef87481b31670066c897bf393","tid":1981383,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:01:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Twitter 國際戰線<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\nTwitter文宣組<br />\n戰線台 @twittermansyunzou <br />\n<br />\nReddit戰線 @reddithk_channel<br />\n文宣 @hkstandstrong_promo_int @guardiansofhongkong<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=03102e32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n做任務，推任務，整圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSXLDyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSXLDyj.jpg&h=86a05172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTEqDx7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTEqDx7.jpg&h=3570731b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ag